Feb 16 (Reuters) - Elastic NV 3E1.F:

  • PRESS RELEASE- ELASTIC AND AMAZON REACH AGREEMENT ON TRADEMARK INFRINGEMENT LAWSUIT

  • ELASTIC NV - RESOLVED ITS DISPUTE WITH AMAZON IN TRADEMARK INFRINGEMENT LAWSUIT RELATED TO TERM "ELASTICSEARCH."

  • ELASTIC - FOLLOWING RESOLUTION, AMAZON HAS BEGUN REMOVING TERM ELASTICSEARCH FROM VARIOUS PAGES ON ITS WEBSITE, SERVICE NAMES, RELATED PROJECT NAMES
